de.iisys.mmis.rssServer

Class RSSSubscription

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.iisys.mmis.rssServer.RSSSubscription

  • public class RSSSubscription
extends java.lang.Object
    The class RSSSubscription represents a subscription of a user of the archive. The user specifies patterns describing conditions for articles of interest. File names of new articles satisfying at least one pattern are provided via notification files stored in the directory specified as the argument of the single constructor.
    Author:
    Richard Goebel
